Introduction

Byeoljji is a South Korean singer, rapper, and dancer under Midas Entertainment. She was a member of the girl group Astell and a former member of the pre-debut girl group Berryz, the girl groups Ndear, and We Girls, and the dance team ZERO. She is also a former member of the pre-debut girl group MIDNIGHT.
